      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·召南·009.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">P'eaou yew mei.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>摽有梅，其實七兮，求我庶士，迨其吉兮。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Dropping are the fruits from the plum-tree;
There are [but] seven [tenths] of them left !
For the gentlemen who seek me,
This is the fortunate time !</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
