        <seg>摽有梅，頃筐塈之，求我庶士，迨其謂之。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Dropt are the fruits from the plum-tree ;
In my shallow basket I have collected them.
Would the gentlemen who seek me
[Only] speak about it !</seg>
